---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Discovery-as-a-Service"
  description="An easier, smarter way to access insight, judgement and momentum â€” on demand"
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/discovery-as-a-service"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Discovery-as-a-Service</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      A lighter, faster alternative to consultants, contractors, and agencies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: Why this model exists -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why this model exists</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Discovery work often gets delayed, rushed, or drowned in slide decks.
          By the time decisions are made, energy is lost, and so is buy-in.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Clarity. flips that. We bring just enough structure, exactly when you
          need it. So you're not waiting weeks for a PowerPoint. You're acting
          on insight fast.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#A7D5F2] dark:bg-[#5AA6D6]">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">With Clarity. you:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-base space-y-2">
          <li>Unblock decisions without hiring a team.</li>
          <li>Keep momentum during uncertainty.</li>
          <li>Get strategic thinking, not busywork.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: How it works -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#75C1E8] dark:bg-[#429EDB] text-white">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">
          Your Support Plan includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-base space-y-2">
          <li>Access to a named Clarity. expert.</li>
          <li>Briefs and Radars tailored to your world.</li>
          <li>Decision-ready input, fast.</li>
          <li>Lightweight tools and sessions as needed.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Strategic support, your way</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Whether you're shaping direction, testing assumptions or aligning
          teams. We're behind you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          No pitches. No onboarding fees. Just thinking partnership, embedded in
          your rhythm.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Compare to legacy models -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-24 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Why not just hire a contractor or agency?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Contractors mean headcount. Agencies mean overhead. Consultants mean
          delays.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Clarity. gives you senior-level input without needing to brief,
          justify or delegate. Just say where you're stuck, and we'll help you
          move.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#429EDB]/10 dark:bg-[#1F78C1]/20">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">Compared to old models:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-base space-y-2">
          <li>No time wasted on outputs you don't need.</li>
          <li>No dependencies on internal headcount.</li>
          <li>No long-term contracts.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Navigation -->
  <section class="my-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      What do our support plans offer?
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-12 justify-center items-center">
      <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/what-you-get"
        aria-label="Previous page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/support-plans"
        aria-label="Next page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
